Package com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.magstripe

Provides access to internal and external magnetic stripe readers.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MagStripeListener
    The MagStripeListener can be used to receive MagStripeData from the MagStripeReader when a magnetic stripe card has been scanned.
    MagStripeReader
    MagStripeReader This interface would represent the magstripe itself.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MagStripeData
    MagStripeData is received upon scanning of a magnetic stripe card.
    MagStripeReaderManager
    MagStripeReaderManager is used to get access to magstripe readers.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MagStripeException
    MagStripeException is thrown if there is any issue in the operation of or in communication to the magnetic stripe card reader.

Package com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.magstripe Description

Provides access to internal and external magnetic stripe readers.
